Clerics who take the Illusion domain seek to weave illusions and confound the enemy, and are granted spells that reflect their deceitful nature.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Spell Focus Illusion: The cleric is better able to deceive enemies.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Mirror Image (2), Displacement (3), Phantasmal Killer (4), Weird(9)</i>.